          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/2371902/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '2371902', 'pos': 9, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})" class="">
            余嘉锡论学杂著（两册）
          </a>
        </dd>
      </dl>
        <dl class="clear"></dl>
  </div>
</div>

  






